		return acc;

	{ name: "CH-time-zone", actual: String(Intl.DateTimeFormat().resolvedOptions().timeZone), value: cookies["CH-time-zone"] != null ? cookies["CH-time-zone"] : encodeURIComponent("UTC") }

		}
	}
	if (cookieChanged) window.location.reload();
}
